me":"2016-12-19T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本好似有出d封住個口既貼<br />\n逼你用鼻抖氣就冇鼻寒<br />\n但香港搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會手動封住佢個口囉<br />\n但好驚佢死<br />\n因為佢個鼻係塞既<br />\n<br />\n同埋我冇得訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05a6cdd23640bc60bfa89342ea88eb8b797b619","tid":45632,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b148d4fffc58b6f9d35981b2768b64477e3e275","tid":45632,"uid":21134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾個月睇醫生話我鼻骨偏右搞到啲氣唔通順<br />\n可以選擇做手術移番正佢 可能會無咁大鼻寒<br />\n<br />\n但係到而家都未約去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無咩其他方法可以唔做手術而減輕鼻寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我男朋友都係咁，佢要帶牙膠瞓覺先無咁大鼻鼾<br />\n想知除左做手術，仲有咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙膠係防磨牙咋下嘛"},{"pid":"6e2c580f039ded7128a5599f08a39cb4a4d4530b","tid":45632,"uid":29358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"我都想問下，我正常身型，平時有做下運動,玩下street workout<br />\n但經常有鼻寒，而且重要勁大聲，老竇老母話十足成個飛機引擎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9e51413b9e514db5c18de084c3920a32405e74","tid":45632,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想問下，我正常身型，平時有做下運動,玩下street workout<br />\n但經常有鼻寒，而且重要勁大聲，老竇老母話十足成個飛機引擎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bf088db9a3672a077068ecf010b1002ad47a1